'Shukla!'

00:20:45.880 --> 00:20:47.640 line:20%
'Hentikan!  - Syukla!'

00:20:48.080 --> 00:20:50.320 line:20%
'Sang Dewi ada di sini!
Sang Dewi ada di sini!'

00:20:50.520 --> 00:20:52.440 line:20%
'Shukla!'

00:20:54.280 --> 00:20:56.920 line:20%
'Salam Ibu Dewi!'

00:20:57.280 --> 00:20:59.440 line:20%
'Bawa Shukla ke hadapanku!'

00:20:59.760 --> 00:21:01.400 line:20%
'Tenanglah, Dewi.'

00:21:01.440 --> 00:21:03.000 line:20%
'Dia telah berdosa!'

00:21:03.280 --> 00:21:04.680 line:20%
'Dia telah melakukan
dosa besar!'

00:21:05.200 --> 00:21:08.680 line:20%
'Dia telah memaksa seorang wanita yang
diceraikan untuk tinggal di rumah ini.'

00:21:08.960 --> 00:21:10.640 line:20%
'Langkahnya adalah dosa!'